# Solution

Context()->texStrings;
BEGIN_SOLUTION;
$PAR
$BBOLD  SOLUTION $EBOLD
$PAR
a) $BR
\( V=BLu=$V V \) $BR
\( I=\frac{f}{BL}=$I A\)$BR
\(Vt=RI+V=$Vt V \) $BR

b) $BR
\(P=V_tI=$P W\) $BR

c) $BR
\(I=\frac{V_t}{R}=$Is A\) $BR

d)
Repeat the similar process for \( \frac{B}{2}\), $BR
\(v_1=$u1 m/s\)

END_SOLUTION
